You are able to associate an Affects or FixVersion with an issue, but when you view the issue you can't tell if the version has been released or not. 

This is especially problematic when you close an issue with a fixVersion. Users can't tell if that version has been released yet without going to the project Version page to see the status of the version. !versionreleasestatus.png|thumbnail!

I propose adding the box icon to the versions on the issue page so you can easily see the state of the versions this issue is tied to.

