JIRA 4.1.1 shows ~350KB to load a dashboard of a new instance with 3 issues created, while JIRA 6.3.15 shows ~1.1MB to load a dashboard in a new instance _without_ any project/issues created. HAR files attached from 4.1.1, 4.4.5 and 6.3.15.

